        </ul>

        <h2>14. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>This Privacy Policy is governed by the laws of <strong>Malaysia</strong>. Any disputes arising from the use of the CLASSIC CNF app will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Malaysia.</p>

        <h2>15. Acknowledgment</h2>
        <p>By using the CLASSIC CNF app, you acknowledge that you have <strong>read, understood, and agreed</strong> to this Privacy Policy.</p>

        <p><strong>Thank you for using CLASSIC CNF!</strong></p>
